has a smile on his face

00:14.180 --> 00:17.775
And he's shining a salute
to the American race

00:20.620 --> 00:23.987
Oh, boy
it's swell to say

00:24.090 --> 00:26.752
Good morning, U.S.A.

00:28.695 --> 00:31.960
Good morning, U.S.A.

00:34.968 --> 00:37.766
- Shoot him! Shoot him!

00:37.871 --> 00:40.203
Big Bird, just share it
with Cookie Monster.

00:40.306 --> 00:43.707
Don't trust him! He just pretends to eat
cookies, but he never swallows anything.

00:44.510 --> 00:46.142
Good morning.

00:46.246 --> 00:49.704
Francine, your negligee is see-through.
Unfortunately, you are not.

00:49.816 --> 00:54.446
Oh, Stan, doesn't today
have some special significance for you?

00:54.554 --> 00:56.454
Today? Wait!

00:56.556 --> 00:58.615
- Is today the 14th?
- Yes. Yes, it is.

00:58.725 --> 01:02.058
Good God! How could I forget a date
so dear to my heart?

01:02.162 --> 01:04.562
It's the big C.I.A.
Fishing trip.

01:08.001 --> 01:09.901
You're gonna do
the laundry anyway, right?

01:10.003 --> 01:13.131
Hmm! No time to poop.
I'll just do it on the way down the stairs.

01:13.239 --> 01:15.139
You're gonna
vacuum anyway, right?

01:17.110 --> 01:19.203
See you, Mom. I'm going to the mall
to try and figure out...

01:19.312 --> 01:21.246
how the piano store
stays in business.

01:21.347 --> 01:23.247
Hold up, Steve.
I'm going with.

01:23.349 --> 01:25.249
Whoa, Roger.
You know you can't leave the house.

01:25.351 --> 01:29.151
- Everyone else gets to.
- Well, everyone else isn't an alien, now are they?

01:29.255 --> 01:33.316
Whoa! Somebody had a big piece
of grouchy pie this morning.

01:33.426 --> 01:36.190
I just can't believe
Stan forgot our anniversary.

01:36.296 --> 01:39.732
- I would never forget our anniversary.
- We have an anniversary?

01:39.833 --> 01:42.927
October 25, the day you forgot
to put on underpants.

01:43.036 --> 01:46.096
Let's celebrate early.
Quick! Straddle mein bowl.

01:50.043 --> 01:53.535
Hayley, do Mommy a favor and put on
something less revealing.

01:53.646 --> 01:56.240
There is nothing inappropriate
about this outfit.

01:56.349 --> 01:59.284
Not if you're gonna spend
the weekend tinkling on Bob Guccione.

01:59.385 --> 02:01.853
Oh, God, Mom.
Were you ever cool?

02:01.955 --> 02:06.551
Oh, yeah, Hayley? Well, I pity
the fool who thinks I'm uncool.

02:06.659 --> 02:09.924
Get it? I was making
a Dr. "T" reference.

02:10.029 --> 02:12.224
Hey, Hayley, guess where
I'm taking you this weekend.

02:12.332 --> 02:15.233
Burning man

02:16.536 --> 02:18.436
It's this awesome celebration...

02:18.538 --> 02:20.438
where they burn
this huge wooden man.

02:20.540 --> 02:22.565
It's all about life, love
and the power of community.

02:22.675 --> 02:24.575
No, it's all about
a bunch of naked morons...

02:24.677 --> 02:26.736
drinking and doing
lots of drugs.

02:26.846 --> 02:28.905
- What are we, 12?
- Wait. Before you decide-

02:29.015 --> 02:33.281
This is a microcosm
of the power that is Burning Man.

02:38.691 --> 02:42.149
Imagine this, but 70 feet tall.

02:42.262 --> 02:44.423
Ah, nothing like the great outdoors.

02:44.531 --> 02:46.431
Who's ready to do
some fishing?

02:46.533 --> 02:48.433
Yeah, yeah!
Let's go fish! Yeah.

02:48.535 --> 02:51.129
This is Cast Master One.
Bring in air support.

02:56.509 --> 02:58.739
Look, it's Ariel.

02:58.845 --> 03:02.611
- Hey, Jackson, you ever do it with a dead mermaid?
- Mermaid? No.

03:04.751 --> 03:07.845
Oh, my God.
Lindsay Coolidge.

03:07.954 --> 03:10.081
Could she be any sexier?

03:14.627 --> 03:17.221
