a dozen Ping-Pong balls?

03:19.566 --> 03:21.466
Hey, Steve,
she's coming this way.

03:21.568 --> 03:23.661
Ask her out-
unless you're afraid.

03:23.770 --> 03:27.035
You forget yourself, Snot.
Steve Smith is never afraid.

03:28.474 --> 03:30.374
I'm Steve Smith.
Would you like to go out with me?

03:30.476 --> 03:32.376
- I'd love to.
- Really?

03:32.478 --> 03:34.571
