doesn't want to go home.

04:37.677 --> 04:39.577
Yeah, I'm, uh, laying low.

04:39.679 --> 04:41.579
Today is the anniversary
of a huge fight...

04:41.681 --> 04:43.581
me and Francine
got into last year.

04:43.683 --> 04:46.083
- Yeah? What about?
- Oh, I forgot our anniversary.

04:46.185 --> 04:49.416
I'm never gonna do that again.

04:49.522 --> 04:51.922
I- Uh-

04:53.026 --> 04:54.926
Ahh!

04:57.030 --> 04:59.123
There it is.

04:59.233 --> 05:02.433
Oh, good. You're up.

05:02.535 --> 05:04.935
I, uh, have a special
anniversary surprise for you.

05:05.038 --> 05:06.938
Your favorite song...

05:07.040 --> 05:09.201
