Whitney Houston.

05:09.309 --> 05:11.402
Come on, daddy.
I- I need my fix.

05:11.511 --> 05:15.208
Remember the deal, Whitney. First you
sing, then you get your precious cocaine.

05:15.315 --> 05:17.215
How dare you!
Do you think I would-

05:24.824 --> 05:26.883
Happy anniversary,
sweetheart.

05:26.993 --> 05:28.893
Come on, Whitney.
Go get it.

05:30.730 --> 05:33.062
What a performer.
Well, let's turn in.

05:33.166 --> 05:35.532
You know what?
If you don't get why this day...

05:35.635 --> 05:38.399
is so important to me,
I guess you never will.

05:38.504 --> 05:40.404
Sweetie, I made a mistake.

05:40.506 --> 05:43.236
Can't you take a page from that bitch
Hillary Clinton and just let it go?

05:43.343 --> 05:46.904
No! This is the most inconsiderate thing
you've ever done.

05:47.013 --> 05:49.243
I am never
going to forget this.

05:49.349 --> 05:51.249
I was afraid
you were gonna say that-

05:51.351 --> 05:53.251
which is why
I got you this card.

05:53.353 --> 05:55.253
Open it. I promise it'll
make everything better.

05:55.355 --> 05:58.188
There's nothing that could- Oh.

06:01.060 --> 06:03.528
