totally meet Def Leppard.

06:15.041 --> 06:18.033
- Def Leppard?
- Francine, what year is it?

06:18.144 --> 06:20.977
Duh. 1985.
Hey, anybody got some gum?

06:21.080 --> 06:23.275
I wanna get the taste
of roadie out of my mouth.

06:25.385 --> 06:28.377
- Why the hell does my wife think it's 1985?
- Huh.

06:28.488 --> 06:30.388
Instead of erasing
the last 20 hours...

06:30.490 --> 06:33.050
I must have erased
the last 20 years.

06:33.159 --> 06:35.923
Oh, I guess this
is the dial for hours...

06:36.028 --> 06:39.555
and this is the dial for years.
Yeah. Yeah.

06:44.237 --> 06:47.070
The last 20 years of your wife's
memory have been erased.

06:47.173 --> 06:49.073
Well, go ahead
and undo it.

06:49.175 --> 06:51.575
Reverse brain erasing?
Now that's just science fiction.

06:51.677 --> 06:53.577
Kind of like
the female orgasm.

06:59.051 --> 07:01.611
Oh, that's great. You gotta
do stand-up. You gotta. You're great.

07:01.721 --> 07:03.689
You know, you're not
the first person who's told me that.

07:03.790 --> 07:05.690
I bet I'm not.
I bet I'm not.

07:05.792 --> 07:08.522
Anyway, Stan,
the procedure is irreversible.

07:08.628 --> 07:10.528
- You're kidding.
- Fraid not.

07:10.630 --> 07:13.360
