Mom's memory?

07:23.509 --> 07:25.409
Well, that's just what the experts
at the lab say...

07:25.511 --> 07:27.445
but there's no way
she could ever forget me.

07:27.547 --> 07:29.777
I mean, who could forget this?
Or this?

07:29.882 --> 07:33.283
Or these?
Go on, kids, give 'em a squeeze.

07:33.386 --> 07:35.445
- It's not weird. I'm your dad.
- She's coming to.

07:35.555 --> 07:39.787
One look at me and her memories
of our love will come flooding back.

07:40.993 --> 07:42.893
Narc! Narc!

07:42.995 --> 07:44.895
What? What?
Oh, God, is there a bee on me?

07:44.997 --> 07:46.965
Oh! Does it look Africanized?

07:47.066 --> 07:48.727
Hey, baby.

07:48.835 --> 07:50.530
Mom.

07:50.636 --> 07:52.536
You idiot.
Why would you do that?

07:52.638 --> 07:54.538
I thought it was
like the hiccups.

07:57.176 --> 07:59.076
Okay, this is gonna be
harder than I thought.

07:59.178 --> 08:01.078
Maybe we should
watch the video.

08:02.415 --> 08:05.077
Has your loved one's memory
been irretrievably lost?

08:05.184 --> 08:07.516
Hi. I'm forgettable actor
Bill Pullman.

08:07.620 --> 08:09.520
You might not remember me
from such movies...

08:09.622 --> 08:11.647
as While You Were Sleeping
and Twister.

08:11.757 --> 08:14.954
Wait. Was I in Twister?
No. No, that was Bill Paxton.

08:15.061 --> 08:17.029
See? Memory can be
pretty tricky...

08:17.129 --> 08:19.188
so that's why if you tell your loved one
what's happened to them...

08:19.298 --> 08:21.198
their brain will implode.

08:21.300 --> 08:23.200
Good luck.
I'm Bill Pullman.

08:23.302 --> 08:25.270
Oh, oh!
I was also in Independence D-

08:25.371 --> 08:27.271
Jeff Daniels is right.

08:27.373 --> 08:29.807
We have to maintain the illusion
that your mother is still 18...

08:29.909 --> 08:32.275
or it's going to get
very messy in there.

08:32.378 --> 08:35.541
- So what do we do?
- Well, when she was 18,
she lived in West Langley...

08:35.648 --> 08:38.048
so we need to get her
back into her old apartment.

08:38.150 --> 08:40.345
Hayley, you can keep an eye on her
by being her roommate.

08:40.453 --> 08:43.820
What? I don't want to live with Mom.
Besides, I'm sure someone lives there.

08:45.958 --> 08:47.983
Good day, ma'am.
I'm a friend of your child.

08:48.094 --> 08:50.062
He or she has asked me
to take you...

08:50.162 --> 08:53.757
- to a wonderful retirement home.
- How lovely.

08:53.866 --> 08:57.199
- Right in here, ma'am.
- Oh, you're such a nice young-

08:59.505 --> 09:03.032
Hello? Am I supposed to vote now?

09:04.911 --> 09:07.004
Please, Pete?
Lindsay won't go out with me...

09:07.113 --> 09:09.172
unless I find a date
for her friend.

09:09.282 --> 09:12.342
She's not that bad-looking-
and besides, you're blind.

09:12.451 --> 09:14.851
Come on. You went
to the Winter Ball with that guy.

09:14.954 --> 09:16.854
Yes, it was a guy.

09:16.956 --> 09:19.015
Hello?

09:19.125 --> 09:22.720
It's like there's not a human being alive
that would go out with that girl.

09:22.828 --> 09:25.490
Hello.

09:27.266 --> 09:29.393
Who are you?

09:29.502 --> 09:32.027
Uh, Hayley,
your new roommate.

09:32.138 --> 09:37.235
- Oh, right. I must have blacked out.
- Wait a second. You party?

09:37.343 --> 09:40.779
Totally.
I need a shower.

09:40.880 --> 09:44.372
- Great Grizzly Adams. Who fired the gardener?

09:44.483 --> 09:48.351
Unbelievable. How did she
ever hook up with a stiff like Dad?

09:48.454 --> 09:50.388
I'll tell you how
she hooked up with a stiff like me.

09:50.489 --> 09:52.514
It was 20 years ago.

09:52.625 --> 09:56.322
I didn't normally pick up transients,
but for her I made an exception.

09:56.429 --> 09:58.363
Her T-shirt said "Bad Girl"...

09:58.464 --> 10:01.092
and her eyes said, "Read the T-shirt."

10:01.200 --> 10:05.569
My God, she was beautiful.
She was cold to me, but I was hot for her-

10:05.671 --> 10:08.105
which explained the moderate
temperature in the car.

10:08.207 --> 10:10.266
And then, fate scampered
across the road.

10:13.045 --> 10:15.741
It was on a slow train to Death City...

10:15.848 --> 10:18.908
so I asked the conductor ifhe could skip
the next few stops to make up-

10:19.018 --> 10:22.112
Oh, I shot it in the eye.

10:22.221 --> 10:25.054
She said it was the most compassionate act
she'd ever witnessed-

10:25.157 --> 10:27.057
and I got to kill something.

10:27.159 --> 10:29.059
It was a magical moment.

10:29.161 --> 10:32.653
Well, there you go. If you want
Francine back, just recreate that moment.

10:32.765 --> 10:35.757
Roger, you're a genius!
That's how I'll bring back her memory.

10:35.868 --> 10:39.804
You just gave me
my reach-around.

10:41.240 --> 10:43.868
Hey, old lady, party!

10:45.311 --> 10:48.109
Wow.

10:48.214 --> 10:50.478
This is Upstanding Conservative
to Dirty Liberal.

10:50.583 --> 10:52.813
Drop point ahead.

10:52.918 --> 10:55.580
Can you check the back tire?
The car is riding kind of low.

10:56.689 --> 10:59.783
What the hell?
You crazy bitch!

10:59.892 --> 11:02.224
I love you!
You got me.

11:02.328 --> 11:04.626
Game on.

11:07.066 --> 11:09.728
- Need a ride?
- Thanks, pops.

11:09.835 --> 11:13.134
Hey, are you, like, a narc? I feel like
I've seen you somewhere before.

11:13.239 --> 11:15.173
- Nope, first time we've met, Francine.
- What?

11:15.274 --> 11:17.174
- Nothing. Stick of your favorite gum?
- What?

11:17.276 --> 11:18.573
Nothing.

11:20.846 --> 11:23.906
Look out!

11:24.016 --> 11:26.576
Oh, sweet masked bandit of nature...

11:26.686 --> 11:28.586
let me put you out of your misery.

11:28.688 --> 11:31.748
Actually, I don't think you hit it.

11:31.857 --> 11:33.950
No, he's suffering- pure agony.

11:34.060 --> 11:35.960
Oh, my God! Stop!

11:36.062 --> 11:37.962
What, are you crazy?

11:38.064 --> 11:40.692
Crazy with compassion.
Come on. Watch me blow its head off.

11:44.737 --> 11:47.262
Die! Die!
So that you may know peace.

11:57.116 --> 11:59.846
- Truck!

12:04.390 --> 12:06.449
Stop the car,
you psychopath!

12:22.842 --> 12:24.742
Oh, God!

12:29.281 --> 12:30.646
Raccoon!

12:33.619 --> 12:35.519
No, I'm never coming home.

12:35.621 --> 12:37.555
Because you're
smothering me, Linda.

12:42.027 --> 12:45.258
I was wrong.
I'll be home by 9:00.

12:45.364 --> 12:49.323
Because I promised Derek
I'd meet him for a drink. That's why 9:00!

12:58.344 --> 13:00.972
And let the love
come flowing back.

13:04.049 --> 13:06.074
Stay away from me!

13:20.065 --> 13:21.396
This is great.

13:21.500 --> 13:24.560
By the way, great call
on this Rasta disguise, Steve.

13:24.670 --> 13:26.797
I'm "ganja" wear it
all the time.

13:28.908 --> 13:30.808
Hey, Steve,
is this your friend?

13:30.910 --> 13:32.810
Yeah. Lindsay,
this is Roger.

13:32.912 --> 13:34.812
- Nice to meet you.
- Charmed.

13:34.914 --> 13:37.974
- And this is Jewel.
- Your date.

13:38.083 --> 13:40.210
Oh, God. Oh, God.
I'm out. I'm out. Ew! Ew!

13:40.319 --> 13:42.219
Hey, we had a deal.

13:42.321 --> 13:46.257
Steve, she's so ugly.

13:46.358 --> 13:49.589
So ugly.

13:49.695 --> 13:52.095
