was taken on our honeymoon.

14:06.478 --> 14:10.278
It's the only photo of Francine
where you can't see Vaj.

14:10.382 --> 14:14.512
Ah, Vaj- the little island boy
who served as our tour guide.

14:14.620 --> 14:18.716
I see from her wristband that you were
at a Sandals all-inclusive resort.

14:19.224 --> 14:20.792
Hmm! Fancy.

14:20.893 --> 14:22.793
Wait a minute.

14:22.895 --> 14:25.022
