the exact spot where he was trapped.

15:04.637 --> 15:07.868
Wow!
You had a boyfriend?

15:07.973 --> 15:11.204
Oh, you have-
You have a little thing.

15:11.310 --> 15:13.210
Oh, Roger, stop it.

15:13.312 --> 15:16.873
- I don't have a hard time looking at you.
- At me?

15:16.982 --> 15:19.041
I can see past
your hydrocephalic head...

15:19.151 --> 15:21.210
