I could not hold mein pee-pee.

16:36.562 --> 16:38.894
Honestly, I only went out with you
to getJewel a date...

16:38.998 --> 16:41.967
- but you're a lot less of a dork than I thought.
- Stick around.

16:42.067 --> 16:45.059
I think you'll find
I'm a lot less of everything.

16:45.170 --> 16:48.230
You can do
whatever you want to me.

16:48.340 --> 16:52.242
Oh, so I can crate you and hide you
in that warehouse at the end of Raiders?

16:52.344 --> 16:55.905
So funny.
Kiss me, funny boy.

16:57.415 --> 16:59.280
I know, I know. Bad for the ozone.

17:01.854 --> 17:04.846
Yeah, Burning Man
is great this year.

17:04.957 --> 17:08.358
Ow! Ow!

17:08.460 --> 17:10.359
Dad, we've been searching all night.

17:10.462 --> 17:12.362
Let's just start fresh
in the morning.

17:12.464 --> 17:14.364
Francine? Francine?

17:14.465 --> 17:16.366
I'm not just saying this
to be clever-

17:16.468 --> 17:18.628
I really feel like a fish
out of water here.

17:21.607 --> 17:23.199
What's the deal
with the flower?

17:23.308 --> 17:26.367
On our wedding day, I placed this yellow
flower in your mom's white bouquet.

17:26.478 --> 17:30.209
It symbolized her sunshine brightening
my otherwise cloudy world.

17:30.315 --> 17:33.375
Dad, I've never seen this side of you.
It's so sweet.

17:33.485 --> 17:35.715
Well, if you tell anybody
I'll kill you.

17:37.823 --> 17:39.723
Ah. I'm serious.
I will kill you.

17:39.825 --> 17:41.850
I will reach into your chest,
pull out your beating heart...

17:41.960 --> 17:44.224
and eat it-
all of it, every last bit.

17:44.329 --> 17:46.854
Well, sweet dreams, angel.

17:46.965 --> 17:48.865
l-It's not you.
It's the timing, you know?

17:48.967 --> 17:50.832
I just got out
of a bad relationship.

17:50.936 --> 17:53.564
You're lying.
I'm a loser.

17:53.672 --> 17:56.072
Don't be like that.
You're not a loser.

17:56.175 --> 17:58.735
Think how pretty
you make people look by contrast.

17:58.844 --> 18:00.744
That's a gift.

18:00.846 --> 18:03.041
Gotcha!

18:04.950 --> 18:06.884
Oh, my God!
You're an alien!

18:06.985 --> 18:09.545
Oh, my God.!
Lindsay.! Lindsay.!

18:09.655 --> 18:12.055
- Roger is an ali-

18:12.157 --> 18:14.182
- Roger!
- She was all over me, and my wig fell off...

18:14.293 --> 18:16.523
- and we'd be in big trouble.

18:17.863 --> 18:19.854
Did you see
where they went?

18:19.965 --> 18:22.695
- Who?
- The black guys who did this.

18:26.971 --> 18:28.667
Aah! Mr. Smith!

18:29.574 --> 18:31.208
- Where's my wife?
- She ditched me as soon as we got here.

18:31.310 --> 18:33.870
I just ran away with her
to get a rise out of Hayley.

18:33.979 --> 18:36.379
- Please don't kill me!
- Let me get this straight.

18:36.482 --> 18:39.883
You ran away with my memory-erased mother
to a pagan festival...

18:39.985 --> 18:42.385
- just to get my attention?
- Did it work?

18:42.488 --> 18:45.252
Did it ever!
Mmm!

18:47.526 --> 18:51.053
You know, we're about to go on tour
to Bangkok and Amsterdam...

18:51.163 --> 18:53.222
and this hot piece
of mama's comin' with us.

18:53.332 --> 18:57.063
I am ripped off my ass!

18:59.671 --> 19:00.968
Francine!

19:01.073 --> 19:03.132
- You again?
- Look what I have.

19:03.242 --> 19:05.472
Remember. Please remember.

19:07.412 --> 19:09.312
How long till it kicks in?

19:09.414 --> 19:12.042
Oh, Francine, for God's sake,
we're married. You love me.

19:12.151 --> 19:16.588
Look, you're a stiff. I could never
fall in love with a suit like you.

19:16.688 --> 19:19.953
A suit like me?
Well then, I'll get rid of the suit.

19:21.860 --> 19:24.192
Huh? Huh? Look at me.
Nothing stiff here.

19:24.296 --> 19:28.164
Hey, it's never gonna
happen with us. Never!

19:31.103 --> 19:34.368
Because hang-gliding
makes me feel alive, Linda, okay?

19:41.446 --> 19:43.004
Francine!

19:52.691 --> 19:54.382
Don't worry. I'm leaving.

19:54.493 --> 19:57.223
I just wanted you to be safe.

19:57.329 --> 20:01.060
You're the best thing that ever
happened to me, and I took it for granted.

20:01.166 --> 20:03.225
I'm just happy that-

20:03.335 --> 20:06.896
Uh, that I got the privilege
to be with you for the time that I did.

20:09.007 --> 20:11.237
Okay, my shoes are full.
I better go now.

20:11.343 --> 20:16.337
I love you, Francine.
It's a little late, but happy anniversary.

20:20.652 --> 20:22.847
Remember.

20:25.757 --> 20:28.157
- Stan?
- Francine?

20:28.260 --> 20:33.254
Stan, it was so weird.
And I was alone and confused.

20:33.365 --> 20:36.926
And there was this raccoon,
and I knew who I was again.

20:37.035 --> 20:38.935
Oh, Francine, thank God.

20:39.037 --> 20:42.529
- I love you.
- I love you too, Stan.

20:45.043 --> 20:47.409
That was gross.
I still love you.

20:49.514 --> 20:52.506
Thanks for looking after me.
I'm so embarrassed.

20:52.618 --> 20:56.019
Don't be. You were fun.
In fact, you were cool.

20:57.189 --> 21:00.158
Oh. Hey, funny story.

21:01.526 --> 21:02.925
A little bit longer...

21:03.028 --> 21:05.053
and their last 24 hours
will be completely forgotten.

21:05.163 --> 21:07.222
- Oh, thank God.
- You are not off the hook, mister.

21:07.332 --> 21:09.232
I am deeply disappointed in you.

21:09.334 --> 21:12.770
- Dad, I was with this one.
- Oh. Well, outstanding.

21:46.738 --> 21:48.569
Bye! Have a beautiful time.

